title: Zach LaVine throws down his best preseason dunk (VIDEO)
text:
Zach LaVine throws down his best preseason dunk (VIDEO) Bob Donnan / USA TODAY Sports Oct 21, 2015 at 7:15p ET 0Shares 
There may not be a better dunker in the world than Zach LaVine . And if you believed that LaVine was the best heading into Tuesday night, the Timberwolves ' game against the Bucks did nothing to change your stance on the issue. 
What'd LaVine do? He just threw down maybe the most powerful alley-oop of the preseason. true 
Yep, Zach LaVine didn't lose any of his leaping ability over the summer. Good to know. MORE NEWS: Want stories delivered to you? Sign up for our NBA newsletters. 0
